===Runners-up===

* [[Venice Cup]] (2) 1976, 2013 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[World Team Olympiad|World Olympiad Womens Teams Championship]] (4) 1976, 1984, 1988, 1992

* [[Buffett Cup]] (1) 2012 


